05:32.600 --> 05:34.900
Big fucking deal,
you did what you said you'd do.

05:51.800 --> 05:53.700
All right.

05:53.900 --> 05:56.300
Five minutes of peace.

05:59.400 --> 06:02.600
- Yeah!
- Nice!

06:02.800 --> 06:04.700
- Nice.
- All right.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.400
There you go.

06:11.800 --> 06:13.600
I'm on the train and I still got you.

06:14.000 --> 06:17.100
- <i>You still got me?</i>
- I got you. What are you doing?

06:17.300 --> 06:19.200
<i>You still got me?</i>

06:20.500 --> 06:22.700
Oh, my God.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.100
Baby? Baby?

07:25.400 --> 07:26.700
Give me the cutting key.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.100
Cutting key.

07:45.200 --> 07:49.000
Control Center calling Pelham 123.
Come in, Pelham 123.

07:49.500 --> 07:52.100
Why did you stop?
You're all green ahead.

07:56.300 --> 07:59.400
<i>Control Center calling Pelham 123.</i>

08:00.200 --> 08:02.700
